---
<section class="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="label">The Problem</span>
    <h2>Today, AI is either blind or wasteful</h2>

    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="card problem-card rival">
        <div class="problem-icon">&#128247;</div>
        <h3>Vision (Screenshots)</h3>
        <p>The AI parses pixels to recover information the app already had in structured form. Expensive, lossy, fragile.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Tokens wasted on OCR</li>
          <li>Layout changes break everything</li>
          <li>Can't see what's off-screen</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card problem-card rival">
        <div class="problem-icon">&#128268;</div>
        <h3>Tool Calls (MCP)</h3>
        <p>The AI can act, but it's flying blind. Every observation requires a dedicated tool. No context of what the user sees.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>No awareness of app state</li>
          <li>Hundreds of tools for one app</li>
          <li>Actions without context</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-bridge friend">
      <div class="solution-line"></div>
      <p class="solution-text">SLOP fills the gap — apps <strong>publish what they are</strong> so AI can <strong>see before it acts</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem h2 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .problem-card {
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }
  .problem-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .problem-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .problem-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }
  .problem-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }
  .problem-card li {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
    position: relative;
  }
  .problem-card li::before {
    content: "×";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #f87171;
  }
  .solution-bridge {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
  }
  .solution-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--primary-dim);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-5);
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--primary));
  }
  .solution-text {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .solution-text strong {
    color: var(--primary);
  }
</style>
